First Department,

April, 1945.

(April 2, 1945.) Paul H. Bell et al., Appellants, v. David Sullivan, Individually and as President of Local 32B, Building Service Employees’ International Union, Respondent, et al., Defendants.

Orders unanimously affirmed each, with $10 costs and disbursements. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
